(672, 'Redes de Transporte Óptico (OTN) y Tecnologías Coherentes', 'NN', 'INGENIERIA', 'TIC', 'GENERICO', '09_00GN02_09', 'Conocimiento básico en telecomunicaciones \r\n$ Conocimientos Medios avanzados en redes de transmisión por FO (WDM, OTN)\r\n', '<b> Modulo 1. OTN Introduction </b>\r\n$ <b> OTN Interfaces Structure </b>\r\n$ OTN Definition \r\n$ OTN Features \r\n$ OTN Standards and Their Relationships\r\n$ OTN Hierarchy and Interfaces\r\n$ OTM-n.m Principal Information Containment Relationships\r\n$ OTM-nr.m Principal Information Containment Relationships\r\n$ OTM-0.m Principal Information Containment Relationships\r\n$ OTM-0.mvn Principal Information Containment Relationships\r\n$ Implementation of OTN Function Modules \r\n$ OTU Function Modules \r\n$ OMS Function Modules\r\n$ OTS Function Modules\r\n$ OTM Line Signals \r\n$ Example \r\n$ OTN Network Interfaces\r\n$ <b> OTN Multiplexing and Mapping Structure </b>\r\n$ Electrical-layer Multiplexing and Mapping of ODUk\r\n$ Electrical-layer Multiplexing and Mapping of ODU0\r\n$ Electrical-layer Multiplexing and Mapping of ODU1\r\n$ Electrical-layer Multiplexing and Mapping of ODU2/ODU2e\r\n$ Electrical-layer Multiplexing and Mapping of ODU3/ODU4\r\n$ Electrical-layer Multiplexing and Mapping of ODUflex\r\n$  OTM Multiplexing and Mapping Structure\r\n$  Multiplexing Route at the OTN Optical Layer\r\n$ OTN Bit Rates and Capacity \r\n$ OTUk Frame Rates \r\n$ ODUk Frame Rates\r\n$ OPUk Frame Rates\r\n$ OTN Signal Frame Period\r\n$  ODUk TDM\r\n$ Multiplexing ODU1 Signals into ODU2 Signals \r\n$ Multiplexing ODU1 or ODU2 Signals into ODU3 Signals\r\n$ <b> OTN Overheads </b>\r\n$ Electrical-Layer Overheads of the OTN \r\n$ Overview of Electrical-Layer Overheads of the OTN\r\n$ Frame Alignment Overhead Byte\r\n$ OTUk Overhead Bytes \r\n$ ODUk Overhead Bytes\r\n$ OPUk Overhead Bytes\r\n$ Optical-Layer Overheads of the OTN\r\n$ <b> Modulo 2. 40G/100G Coherent OTU Technology </b>\r\n$ <b> 40G/100G Technology Overview </b>\